        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1190">
<l>pacappeṉap pērpeṟuta ṉaṉṟē nayappittār</l>
<l>nalkāmai tūṟṟā reṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It would be good to be said of me that I have turned sallow, if friends do not reproach with unkindness him who pleased me (then).</l>
            </lg>
